pages = NextFetchModel.collection.order('order_num').fetch(5)
page_list = ['page0', 'page1', 'page2', 'page3', 'page4']
for page in pages:
    assert page.name in page_list
pages.next_fetch()
page_list2 = ['page5', 'page6', 'page7', 'page8', 'page9']
for page in pages:
    assert page.name in page_list2
